<p>Impressions from our Plug and Pay event with <a href="https://generalassemb.ly/hong-kong">General Assembly</a> at the great Sai Ying Pun coworking space Platform.</p>

<p>Focus of the event was to assist people with getting bitcoin wallets and making their first transactions.</p>

<p>The 50 HKD of entrance fee was entirely reimbursed to users in Bitcoin, who could then use them to buy drinks at the bar.</p>

<p>Hong Kong Bitcoin exchange <a href="https://anxbtc.com/">ANX</a> provided us with their Bitcoin ATM.</p>

